==汙染==
[[File:Barb_gonio_080525_9625_ltn.jpg|thumb]]已經消失]]
芝塔龙河污染問題的源頭是[[萬隆|萬隆]]與[[芝馬墟|芝馬墟]]的紡織廠，他們和一些知名國際大廠都有業務往來<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2013/11/06/citarum-kalimantan-world-s-most-polluted.html |title=Citarum, Kalimantan world’s most polluted |author=Nadya Natahadibrata |date=November 6, 2013 |publisher=Jakarta Post |accessdate=9 November 2013 |archive-date=2020-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200815115458/https://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2013/11/06/citarum-kalimantan-world-s-most-polluted.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。由於超過2000家工廠高度集中排放[[有毒廢料|有毒廢料]]，[[鉛|鉛]]、[[汞|汞]]、[[砷|砷]]等有毒化學物質汙染了5020平方公里河域<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.theguardian.com/global-development/2013/nov/08/toxic-towns-poisoned-rivers-byproduct-industry |title=Toxic towns and poisoned rivers: a byproduct of industry for the rich |author=Stephen Leahy |date=November 8, 2013 |publisher=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |accessdate=9 November 2013 |archive-date=2021-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210506031757/https://www.theguardian.com/global-development/2013/nov/08/toxic-towns-poisoned-rivers-byproduct-industry |dead-url=no }}</ref>，使得河水呈現紅、黃、綠、黑等多種顏色。嚴重的水污染使得芝塔龙河大約60%的魚類已經消失<ref name="最髒的河流之一"/>。

由於大約有900萬人居住在芝塔龙河流域，每個人繼續往河裡傾倒垃圾，使得這條河在人類的使用下持續被汙染中<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-460077/Is-worlds-polluted-river.html |title=Is this the world's most polluted river? |author=Richard Shears |date=5 June 2007 |publisher=Mail Online |accessdate=24 May 2010 |archive-date=2010-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100612220523/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-460077/Is-worlds-polluted-river.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Nana Terangna Bukit |year=1995 |title=Water quality conservation for the Citarum River in West Java |journal=Water Science and Technology |publisher=IWA Publishing |volume=31 |issue=9 |pages=pp 1–10 |url=http://www.iwaponline.com/wst/03109/wst031090001.htm |doi= |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070926225134/http://www.iwaponline.com/wst/03109/wst031090001.htm |archivedate=2007-09-26 }}</ref>。當地人依靠芝塔龙河取得飲用及洗滌用水，使得當地的罹癌率上升，各種皮膚病和精神疾病不斷發生<ref name="最髒的河流之一"/>。有人認為，人們根本分不清這究竟是一條河還是一座垃圾場。沿岸居民由於已無法再從河中捕魚，轉而從河裡拾荒變賣<ref name="最髒的河流之一"/>。

在2008年12月5日，[[亞洲開發銀行|亞洲開發銀行]]批准5億美金貸款來清理芝塔龙河，並表示芝塔龙河是世界上最骯髒的河流<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www1.voanews.com/english/news/a-13-2008-12-05-voa15-66736547.html |title=ADB Gives Indonesia $500 Million to Clean Up World's Dirtiest River |author=Nancy-Amelia Collins |date=5 December 2008 |work= |publisher=[[Voice_of_America|voanews.com]] |accessdate=24 May 2010 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100702043107/http://www1.voanews.com/english/news/a-13-2008-12-05-voa15-66736547.html |archive-date=2010-07-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://web.pts.org.tw/titv/news/news_info.php?UID=50904 |title=工業化汙染嚴重 全球十大毒區公布 |access-date=2014-04-11 |archive-date=2018-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180413043225/http://web.pts.org.tw/titv/news/news_info.php?UID=50904 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==復甦==
2011年11月，芝塔龙河開始復原，預計投下35兆[[印尼盾|印尼盾]]（約4億[[美金|美金]]）與15年的時間完成。自芝塔龙河的源頭哇杨文图山（{{lang|id|Wayang-Windu}}）開始復原，經過八個縣與三個市約180公里的距離，前三年的目標是希望能清除1050萬立方公尺的[[沉積物|沉積物]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.pikiran-rakyat.com/node/165108 |title=Rehabilitasi Total Sungai Citarum Butuh Rp 35 Triliun dalam Waktu 15 Tahun |date=November 10, 2011 |access-date=2014-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131111134004/http://www.pikiran-rakyat.com/node/165108 |archive-date=2013-11-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

